102-190a @#/ /dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo/ /oM mo kha mu khi/ tri mu khi/ tri mu khi/ sa ha sra mu khi/ ta thA ga tA mu kha s+t+wi ha na/ tshin+da tshin+da/ b+hin+da b+hin+da/ swa thA nAM gats+tsha slA he swA hA/ mad si dang / brta ka dang / ga gon ring po la lan nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas pa byas te gshags na mtsher pa'i skran zhi bar 'gyur ro/ /the tshom med do/ /skran zhi ba'i gzungs rdzogs s+ho/ /
